Signed-off-by: Lee Jones <lee.jones@linaro.org>
Change-Id: I9bddbb2e75eb5524f387510e463e3f59bedf5fb9
---
 drivers/usb/host/ehci-pci.c | 7 +++++++
 1 file changed, 7 insertions(+)

